        <module id="duine">
            <h>duine</h>
            <p><g>còta air <a href="?gd=duine">duine</a></g>
                <en>a coat on a man, a man with a coat on</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>A bheil còta air an duine? Tha.</gd>
                        <tr>Does the man have a coat on? Yes, he does.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 14</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </module>
